Install PlatformIO
Install shell commands
Install PlatformIO Clion plugin
Select platformio executable in CLion

In CLion run Tools > pio > run init

Build target as shell script:
    pio run -t upload

Install micronucleus...?
    git clone https://github.com/micronucleus/micronucleus.git
cd micronucleus/commandline
sudo apt install libusb-dev
make
sudo make install
